  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nIn order to properly use the bounded actor-based invariant testing pattern outlined here: https://github.com/foundry-rs/book/issues/497#issuecomment-1208473205 the ability to turn off the random caller functionality in invariant testing is required.\r\n\r\nWithout this ability, `revert_on_failure = true` can't be used as successful calls can't be guaranteed.\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_",
